rrent density are provided\nfor specific limiting cases of the physical parameter of the model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Oct 2014 19:55:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Oct 2014 13:24:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 26 Dec 2014 17:16:54 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2015 17:42:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
